@node HowToRegister "ANSI-Draw ... How to register"

This program is released under the concept of ShareWare which means that you
may use this program freely for a period of 30 days. After that you have to
register your personal copy with me.

The registration must be done so I can keep on updating the program. If I
recognize that not many people support the development I will simply stop
releasing further version.

Registration is made by filling in the form below and sending it to me.
A registration fee of 100Sek or 20$ which is to be considered as a gift to
me must be enclosed otherwise I will not register you. The money is meant to
cover the cost of sending you your key and the latest version of the
program, it is also meant to cover the cost of uploading updates and new
versions to BBS's. If the money is not enclosed you will not be registered
and you will not receive anything from me. I do not accept any other
currencies than Sek or Dollar in cash.

The key you will get when registering is your own private and MUST NOT be
given to anyone else. By giving the key to someone else you are breaking this
agreement and are acting as a criminal.

You must give me a delivery time of 5 weeks. If you haven't heard from me
then you may try to contact me and ask why you haven't got your key.
See @{"how to contact the author" link Author}.

This offer is only valid till June 1996.


